Unlikely,
but not impossible.

00:11:34.154 --> 00:11:36.158
[Harunobu]
Are we on the same page?

00:11:36.225 --> 00:11:38.195
<i>[Erika] Tatsuya,</i>
<i>we're over here!</i>

00:11:38.262 --> 00:11:39.498
<i>Come on!</i>

00:11:39.566 --> 00:11:41.302
Hey!
[gasps]

