Thanks.

00:11:54.394 --> 00:11:55.296
[Tatsuya] That's good.

00:11:55.363 --> 00:11:57.802
By the way, Erika,
where's Mikihiko?

00:11:57.868 --> 00:12:00.106
He told us he's feeling under
the weather.

