I may very well have collapsed,
too.

00:12:09.024 --> 00:12:10.293
[audience cheering]
[gasps]

00:12:18.810 --> 00:12:25.791
[beeping]

00:12:27.862 --> 00:12:29.197
[lasers firing]

00:12:34.709 --> 00:12:36.245
Extraordinary.

00:12:36.312 --> 00:12:39.017
Wow, that's Miss Saegusa's
Der Freischutz technique.

00:12:39.484 --> 00:12:41.288
And it's even faster
than last year.

00:12:41.355 --> 00:12:42.324
[banging]

00:12:54.281 --> 00:12:56.620
[buzzing]

00:12:56.686 --> 00:12:58.957
[crowd cheering]

00:13:12.518 --> 00:13:13.854
[all] Cheers!

00:13:14.956 --> 00:13:16.425
Chairwoman,

00:13:16.492 --> 00:13:19.464
congratulations on winning
your speed shooting event today!

00:13:19.532 --> 00:13:21.168
Thank you very much.

00:13:21.435 --> 00:13:22.605
Don't forget Mari.

00:13:22.672 --> 00:13:25.043
She's going
to the Battle Board semifinals.

00:13:25.109 --> 00:13:27.147
For now it's all going
as expected.

00:13:27.213 --> 00:13:28.684
[Mayumi]
And First High School won

00:13:28.750 --> 00:13:30.688
the Speed Shooting event
for boys as well.

00:13:30.754 --> 00:13:33.225
<i>[Mari] Battle Board</i>
<i>was something of a nail‐biter,</i>

00:13:33.292 --> 00:13:35.898
<i>but Hattori sure did manage</i>
<i>to pull that out in the end.</i>

00:13:35.964 --> 00:13:37.267
<i>[Azusa] Maybe the adjustments</i>

00:13:37.334 --> 00:13:39.271
<i>to his CAD weren't working</i>
<i>for him.</i>

00:13:39.338 --> 00:13:41.876
Well, I heard that he's
been tweaking it all day

00:13:41.943 --> 00:13:44.114
with Kenoshita
from the technical staff.

00:13:44.515 --> 00:13:47.253
Fortunately Hanzou
has the whole day off tomorrow.

00:13:47.320 --> 00:13:49.191
I suppose we'll just have
to let him adjust it

00:13:49.257 --> 00:13:50.661
to his heart's content.

00:13:51.295 --> 00:13:54.000
Although, I think
that Kinoshita's busy with

00:13:54.067 --> 00:13:55.671
the girls'
Crowd Ball event tomorrow.

00:13:55.738 --> 00:13:58.242
