a big risk to take, though.

00:14:04.221 --> 00:14:05.824
[Suzune] Then how 'bout
asking Shiba

00:14:05.891 --> 00:14:07.728
to fill in since he's off
both tomorrow

00:14:07.795 --> 00:14:09.231
and the day after?
‐ [grunts]

00:14:09.297 --> 00:14:10.266
[exhales]

00:14:10.333 --> 00:14:12.237
I guess that's our best bet,
huh?

00:14:12.671 --> 00:14:13.740
All right.
Well, Miyuki?

00:14:13.807 --> 00:14:14.642
