on your face?

00:14:42.030 --> 00:14:44.736
Nice try.
Never mind.

00:14:44.802 --> 00:14:46.105
[Tatsuya] Thanks
for letting me know.

00:14:46.873 --> 00:14:48.109
I'll walk you back.

00:14:48.476 --> 00:14:50.881
Oh, no, please.
That's not necessary.

00:14:50.948 --> 00:14:53.486
I can't trouble you more
than this, honestly.

