00:15:11.890 --> 00:15:13.960
[Tatsuya] Yeah,
but at this moment,

00:15:14.027 --> 00:15:15.831
you're a high priority.

00:15:16.131 --> 00:15:18.202
Oh, brother!
Just listen to yourself,

00:15:18.269 --> 00:15:19.572
