I'm more important

00:15:19.639 --> 00:15:20.741
than your work!

00:15:20.808 --> 00:15:22.277
‐ [giggles]
<i>‐ [Tatsuya] That may be true,</i>

00:15:22.343 --> 00:15:24.649
