<i>misunderstood it.</i>

00:15:24.715 --> 00:15:26.151
[chuckles]

00:15:26.218 --> 00:15:27.521
‐ Let's go.
‐ [giggles]

00:15:27.588 --> 00:15:29.324
Yes, I'm coming!

00:15:29.391 --> 00:15:31.395
[Miyuki] Um,
just so you know,

00:15:31.462 --> 00:15:33.332
I feel the same way, brother.

00:15:33.399 --> 00:15:34.434
[Tatsuya] What's that?
[gasps]

00:15:34.502 --> 00:15:35.537
[exhales]

00:15:35.604 --> 00:15:36.673
It's like you said.

00:15:36.739 --> 00:15:39.044
