00:15:49.030 --> 00:15:50.567
[Mayumi] Hey, Tatsuya.

00:15:52.337 --> 00:15:54.107
I'm counting on you today.

00:15:54.675 --> 00:15:55.944
If I may ask,

00:15:56.011 --> 00:15:57.948
are you gonna compete
in that outfit?

00:15:58.015 --> 00:15:59.117
[Mayumi] Yes, I am.

00:16:00.086 --> 00:16:01.523
[gasps]

00:16:01.589 --> 00:16:03.192
Do I look good?

00:16:03.259 --> 00:16:04.896
I think it's cute.

00:16:05.631 --> 00:16:07.835
[chuckles]
It's very becoming on you.

00:16:08.202 --> 00:16:09.471
Oh, you think so?

00:16:09.972 --> 00:16:11.509
[chuckles]
You flatter me.

00:16:11.576 --> 00:16:12.878
[computer beeping]

00:16:12.945 --> 00:16:14.281
[Mayumi grunts]

00:16:15.517 --> 00:16:16.986
Um, Tatsuya.

00:16:17.353 --> 00:16:19.559
Would you mind giving me
a hand with my stretches?

00:16:21.696 --> 00:16:24.602
[footsteps approaching]

00:16:30.446 --> 00:16:32.350
[Mayumi] That's good enough.

00:16:35.524 --> 00:16:36.526
[grunts]

00:16:36.593 --> 00:16:37.561
Hmm?

00:16:38.028 --> 00:16:38.930
[gasps]

00:16:38.997 --> 00:16:40.166
[exhales]

00:16:41.068 --> 00:16:42.270
[grunts]

00:16:42.337 --> 00:16:44.074
Thanks a lot, Tatsuya.

00:16:44.441 --> 00:16:45.611
[Tatsuya] You're very welcome.

00:16:46.546 --> 00:16:47.681
[giggles]

00:16:47.748 --> 00:16:49.619
What a new experience for me.

00:16:49.685 --> 00:16:50.687
[Tatsuya] Huh?

00:16:50.754 --> 00:16:52.123
I have older brothers as well

00:16:52.190 --> 00:16:53.325
as younger sisters,
you see,

00:16:53.392 --> 00:16:54.829
but not a younger brother.

00:16:54.896 --> 00:16:56.231
[Tatsuya] Uh‐huh.

00:16:57.333 --> 00:16:58.803
[Mayumi] How do I put this?

00:16:58.870 --> 00:17:01.441
You know how you never give me
any special treatment?

00:17:01.609 --> 00:17:03.279
I'm not sure what
you're talking about.

00:17:03.345 --> 00:17:05.116
Have I acted improperly
around you?

00:17:06.451 --> 00:17:09.024
No, that's the opposite
of what I'm saying.

00:17:09.090 --> 00:17:10.661
You don't tense up on me.

00:17:10.727 --> 00:17:12.765
You don't get all flustered
or distracted.

00:17:12.831 --> 00:17:14.134
Know what I'm saying?

00:17:14.401 --> 00:17:16.806
So is this what it's like
to have a younger brother?

00:17:17.207 --> 00:17:19.545
I'm just kidding.
[giggles]

00:17:20.647 --> 00:17:22.016
I have no clue.

00:17:22.417 --> 00:17:24.522
All I've got
is a younger sister.

00:17:25.122 --> 00:17:26.693
That's true.
You make a good point.

00:17:27.193 --> 00:17:28.462
Apologies.

00:17:28.763 --> 00:17:31.168
I should check in to see how
the other athletes are doing.

00:17:31.235 --> 00:17:32.638
Pardon me.

00:17:32.705 --> 00:17:33.573
[Mayumi] Smart thinking.

00:17:33.640 --> 00:17:34.709
[Izumi]
That won't be necessary.

00:17:34.775 --> 00:17:36.178
[both grunting]

00:17:39.384 --> 00:17:41.121
[Mayumi] Oh, hey there,
Izumin.

00:17:41.188 --> 00:17:42.625
Miss Saegusa,

00:17:42.691 --> 00:17:44.394
how many times do I have
to ask you not

00:17:44.461 --> 00:17:45.931
to call me that name already?

00:17:46.331 --> 00:17:50.439
Anyway, what did you mean,
"It won't be necessary?"

00:17:50.807 --> 00:17:52.745
Oh, right.
Hi, Shiba.

00:17:53.112 --> 00:17:56.084
You can just stay here
and watch Miss Saegusa's match.

00:17:56.151 --> 00:17:58.556
I can take care
of the remaining athletes.

00:17:59.024 --> 00:18:00.092
Sure, if you say so.

00:18:00.159 --> 00:18:01.529
That sounds like a good plan.

00:18:01.930 --> 00:18:03.132
I'll see you later.

00:18:08.142 --> 00:18:09.612
Oh.

00:18:10.514 --> 00:18:12.818
[Mayumi] She's really not
a bad kid, you know, but...

