[gun cocking]

00:18:28.717 --> 00:18:30.821
[magical whooshing]

00:18:39.805 --> 00:18:40.841
[Misato exhales]

00:18:41.776 --> 00:18:42.845
[giggles]

00:18:42.911 --> 00:18:45.684
[crowd cheering]

