[buzzing]

00:19:15.242 --> 00:19:16.278
[grunts]

00:19:16.345 --> 00:19:17.581
[magical whooshing]
[groans]

00:19:18.215 --> 00:19:19.417
Ah!

00:19:21.288 --> 00:19:22.658
Landline Sourcing.

00:19:22.725 --> 00:19:23.660
Right.

00:19:23.727 --> 00:19:25.162
Her family's skilled
in long range

00:19:25.229 --> 00:19:26.966
solid matter
vibration type magic.

00:19:27.033 --> 00:19:29.471
<i>[Kei] The Chiyoda's specialty</i>
<i>is casting spells</i>

