<i>As far as strategies go,</i>

00:20:21.241 --> 00:20:22.911
<i>I don't think it's a bad one.</i>

00:20:22.978 --> 00:20:25.617
[buzzing]
[crowd cheering]

00:20:25.684 --> 00:20:27.821
[inhales sharply]
Victory!

00:20:28.255 --> 00:20:29.992
[grunts, chuckles]

00:20:30.059 --> 00:20:31.996
[giggles]

