[knocking]

00:21:30.780 --> 00:21:32.183
<i>[Miyuki] Brother, it's me.</i>

00:21:32.250 --> 00:21:34.487
Would it be all right
if I came in for a little while?

00:21:34.555 --> 00:21:36.258
[Tatsuya] Sure thing.

00:21:36.893 --> 00:21:39.030
I hope I'm not
interrupting anything.

00:21:39.565 --> 00:21:41.134
Hey, we came over to hang out.

00:21:41.201 --> 00:21:42.370
We're sorry to intrude.

00:21:42.838 --> 00:21:44.374
[both] Thanks
for having us over.

00:21:44.440 --> 00:21:45.610
[Leonhard] Hey, let me through.

00:21:46.077 --> 00:21:47.146
<i>[Hanzou] Excuse me.</i>

